steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"dr3un","text":"Set up the culture(s) in 500 mL flasks.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6uo6l","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fvsfg","text":"Example: ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":9}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2jmep","text":"100 ml 2X YPD culture — starting OD600 of 2.0","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"dvvfv","text":"Use C1V1=C2V2 to calculate the amount of O/N cells you need to add to 100 ml for a starting OD600 of ______. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"89m7c","text":"Grow the inoculated cultures on a platform shaker at 30°C and 270 rpm for 4 hours.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2bj42","text":"Put sterile water on ice and place at 4°C.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":4,"length":13}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ca7ih","text":"~100 mL of sterile water needed per reaction.  ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"58co3","text":"Prepare electroporation buffer and put in ice at 4°C.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":8,"length":21}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7qsl2","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1g91h","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"66qid","text":"500 mL Electroporation buffer: ~100 mL needed per reaction","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":58}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"45gk","text":"Add 250 mL 2M Sorbitol to a sterile 500 mL bottle","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cjkom","text":"Add 5 mL 100 mM CaCl2","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"54a3b","text":"Bring volume to 500 mL with sterile water.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6epgr","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d50r3","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7ll8l","text":"Collect yeast cells by centrifugation at 1500 g for 3 minutes and remove the media.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":41,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"49isd","text":"2-50 ml conical tubes - 50 ml each ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"11vi","text":"Prepare conditioning buffer during spins- 0.1 M LiAc/10 mM DTT.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":8,"length":19},{"style":"bold","offset":42,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ep5j2","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"75a72","text":"Conditioning Buffer: 20 mL needed per reaction","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":46}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"56c7u","text":"Add 50 mL sterile water to a sterile 250 mL sterile bottle","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7vsog","text":"Add 5 mL 2M Lithium Acetate","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6i5a3","text":"Add 1000 ul 1M DTT","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fhloj","text":"Bring volume to 100 mL (44 mL sterile water added with a serological pipette)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9r9r4","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a0pkm","text":"Put any remaining conditioning buffer in a well labeled 50 mL conical tube for disposal with EHS. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":0,"length":96}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"dpkva","text":"Wash the cell pellets with 25 mL ice-cold water.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6h63i","text":"50 ml conical tubes - 25 ml each","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":21,"length":1}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"biesq","text":"Spin at 1500 g for 3 minutes and remove the media.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":8,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3eimo","text":"Wash the cell pellets again with 25 mL ice-cold water.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9d5v9","text":"50 ml conical tubes - 25 ml each","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"g3u7","text":"Spin at 1500 g for 3 minutes and remove the media.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":8,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7u5uh","text":"Wash the cell pellet with 25 mL of ice-cold electroporation buffer (1M Sorbitol / 1 mM CaCl2)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":68,"length":24}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"f63um","text":"50 ml conical tubes - 25 ml each","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3vk2m","text":"Spin at 1500 g for 3 minutes and remove the media.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":8,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7u5ur","text":"Condition the yeast cells by re-suspending the cell pellet in 10 mL 0.1 M LiAc/10 mM DTT.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":62,"length":27}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d6ume","text":"50 ml conical tubes - 10 ml each","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":5},{"style":"bold","offset":22,"length":10}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"n6nr","text":"Pool the tubes culture into one flask for the outgrowth.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c5f78","text":"10 ml of conditioning buffer for each tube, then pool in a 125 mL flask.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":2,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7pd3r","text":"Shake at 270 rpm in a culture flask for 30 minutes at 30 °C.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":59}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"kedf","text":"Pour cells into a 50 mL conical tube.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ft08a","text":"Collect the conditioned cells by centrifugation (1500g for 3 minutes).","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":49,"length":19}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"e1fo9","text":"Wash the cells once with 50 mL ice-cold electroporation buffer.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8dlqh","text":"Spin at 1500 g for 3 minutes and remove the media.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":8,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7hgoe","text":"Re-suspended the cell pellet in 100 to 200 μL electroporation buffer to reach a final volume of 1 mL.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":32,"length":13}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8umtj","text":"Record the volume needed to get to 1 mL","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5jre9","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bctdm","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7o9e1","text":"Example: 700 ul cell pellet + 300 ul electroporation buffer = 1 mL","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":9}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1jdqp","text":"2 electroporation reactions of 400 μl each.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":42}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6q91a","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cavb2","text":"You may need to add more electroporation buffer to reach 1 mL cell mixture. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":76}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"baj9o","text":"If only doing 1 transformation, less volume can be added as only 400 ul is needed per transformation. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"bot5l","text":"The cells are kept on ice until electroporation.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":48}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"aeun9","text":"Pre-chill BioRad GenePulser cuvette(s) (0.2 cm electrode gap).","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3hlaa","text":"1 cuvette per transformation ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"1icsl","text":"Prepare enough outgrowth media for all your samples:  1:1 1M sorbitol: 2X YPD","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":54,"length":23}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"v5j4","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8akre","text":"8 mL per sample aliquoted into 50 ml conical tubes.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"eg6p6","text":"Use 1 ug of plasmid DNA per 400 ul of cells.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":4,"length":4}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9ib3f","text":"Add ____ uL of plasmid DNA to the 1 mL of cells = 1 ug per 400 uL.  ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ed0im","text":"2.5 ug of plasmid DNA in 1 mL of cells.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4bh2e","text":"Gently mix 400 μl electrocompetent cells and DNA and transfer to a pre-chilled BioRad GenePulser cuvette (0.2 cm electrode gap). ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":11,"length":6}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5rptv","text":"Kept on ice for 5 minutes until electroporation.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"fvh2i","text":"Electroporate the cells at 2.5 kV and 25 μF. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":23}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fsq7v","text":"Typical time constant ranges from 3.0 to 4.5 milliseconds.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e3qls","text":"200 Ohms","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"cjksb","text":"Using a sterile pasteur pipette, transfer electroporated cells from each cuvette into 8 mL of 1:1 mix of 1 M sorbitol : 2X YPD media. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":86,"length":46}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"evbc9","text":"Incubate the 50 mL conical tube containing the 8 mL of recovery media in the 30°C standing incubator for 1 hour.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fgsd2","text":"Mix by gentle inversion (~4x) every 15 mins.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4m9et","text":"Use a rack to store 50 mL conical tubes in the incubator. Do not store conical tubes upside down as they tend to leak.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7oqe6","text":"Collect cells by centrifugation (1500g for 3 minutes) and resuspend in SD URA- + 2% glucose. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":33,"length":19}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4rmn8","text":"Use 1 mL SD URA- + 2% glucose media for every 400 μl electroporated cells.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"fn7ki","text":"Prepare 10-fold serial dilutions from the cell suspension and plate 100 μl of 10-2, 10-3, and 10-4 dilutions onto selection plates and incubate at 30 °C incubator for 2 days.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"esq7e","text":"If using an antibiotic marker for selection, let the cells grow on just YPD for 1 days and then replica print onto YPD + antibiotic the following day. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"30iu","text":"Count the number of colonies on each plate to determine the CFUs. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
